name: ImmutableStack_popTest
description: Unit tests for the pop functionality of the ImmutableStack class.

test_cases.name: testPopOnNonEmptyStack
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality on a non-empty stack, ensuring the stack is not empty after popping and the correct element is peeked.

test_cases.name: testPopOnSingleElementStack
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality on a stack with a single element, ensuring the stack becomes empty after popping.

test_cases.name: testPopOnEmptyStack
test_cases.description: Tests the pop functionality on an empty stack, expecting a RuntimeException to be thrown.
